{"tid":512650,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得班NURSING撚好扮野","createTime":"2017-12-28T16:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T05:10:37.000Z","uid":68626,"like":61,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b95ad2e04b047ec31b4ea23ef84953ba6b6600","tid":512650,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T16:55:55.000Z","msg":"明明就係貪份高人工 先狗沖去做<br />\n如果同普通文職仔差唔多人工<br />\n仲有冇咁多人狗沖呀<br />\n明明貪錢講到自己好撚偉大咁<br />\n人地唔識d nursing 野就第一時間衝出黎屌人先<br />\n之後係到拋書包<br />\n之後日日呻自己好撚辛苦<br />\n丫你唔明嫁啦xyz<br />\n正常人又點會明呀<br />\n知我唔明你又呻<br />\n屌你老味呀叔我做地盤仲辛苦啦 咪又係日日收工番屋企訓教<br />\n知唔知咩叫人工包埋呀 收得錢就咪撚呻啦<br />\n諗定下面回覆: 係咪人工高唔呻得？/樓主入唔到nursing成浸酸味/慢慢係到酸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d125de1e365b392d3234bf63d57af1ad837b87","tid":512650,"uid":150611,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T17:00:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79ef98e6730e3b5dfc57d05501ee7102cff43be0","tid":512650,"uid":159166,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T17:00:49.000Z","msg":"樓主翻工唔收錢㗎？"},{"pid":"41c5d19604276e16411cd162185b16fd49513379","tid":512650,"uid":18628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T17:02:06.000Z","msg":"年經"},{"pid":"592aa7fc61e615430e99a79cfe7167cc496c44f2","tid":512650,"uid":138375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T17:02:45.000Z","msg":"睇到厭"},{"pid":"159aa9e88a32c0b9c83ede38621a70f8624d1760","tid":512650,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T17:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>年經</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n月經啦"},{"pid":"f6a6fcac8ab4b93b7e59f3f618e4c13eceb6ed3c","tid":512650,"uid":2080,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T17:04:36.000Z","msg":"護士撚 一句到尾人工得$15000做唔撚做<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0de33ae152078b18ab61e78f7ac1cca276a1b2","tid":512650,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cited